videos.headline: Mikal Bridges gets a steal then a slam dunk in transition
UCF's Tacko Fall fights through multiple post defenders on his way to a dunk
Villanova swats away last shot attempt for UCF
Tacko Fall dunks over Villanova's Kris Jenkins

videos.description: 2H (7:55) UCF Tacko Fall made Dunk. Assisted by Nick Banyard.
videos.headline: T. Fall made Dunk. Assisted by N. Banyard.

videos.description: Villanova starts pulling away from UCF thanks to Mikal Bridges making the steal at mid-court and then going in all alone for a massive two-hand jam.
videos.headline: Bridges with the steal and monster jam for Villanova
